sentences: Olivia Hime (born June 25, 1943) is a Brazilian singer and lyricist.
In 2005, the song Cancao Transparente, composed by Hime and her husband, pianist and composer Francis Hime, was nominated for a Latin Grammy for Best Brazilian Song.
